  "pageTitle": "緊湊且大型的廢棄物處理佈局",
  "bodyHtml": "<main class=\"product-page case-study-detail-page case-study-detail-page-industrial\">\n      <section class=\"section page-hero\" aria-labelledby=\"case-detail-title\">\n        <p class=\"eyebrow\">大型廢棄物箱 詳情</p>\n        <h1 id=\"case-detail-title\">緊湊且大型的廢棄物處理佈局</h1>\n        <p class=\"hero-copy\">此為小型且體積龐大的廢棄物預處理參考，買家需在單一工作流程中完成接收、縮小尺寸、分離及打包輸出。</p>\n      </section>\n\n      <section class=\"section case-detail-section case-detail-timeline-section\" id=\"bulky-waste-processing-layout\" aria-labelledby=\"bulky-waste-processing-layout-timeline-title\">\n        <div class=\"section-heading\">\n          <p class=\"eyebrow\">參考時間軸</p>\n          <h2 id=\"bulky-waste-processing-layout-timeline-title\">從超大型廢棄物處理到緊湊型預處理</h2>\n          <p>案例依買方評估流程排序：背景、合作單位、限制、解決方案，以及前後比較。</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"case-detail-timeline\" aria-label=\"案例 詳情 時間軸\">\n          <article class=\"case-detail-timeline-item\">\n            <div class=\"case-detail-timeline-marker\"><span>01</span></div>\n            <div class=\"case-detail-stage-card\">\n              <p class=\"case-detail-stage-label\">專案背景</p>\n              <h3>超大混合廢棄物需在處理前進行預處理</h3>\n              <p>該佈局透過減少進料尺寸、分離可回收組分及準備殘渣以供下游處理，處理大體積廢棄物與輕質混合廢棄物。</p>\n              <dl class=\"case-detail-metrics\">\n                <div><dt>物料類別</dt><dd><strong class=\"case-detail-metric-value\">2 串流</strong><span>大塊與輕質混合廢棄物</span></dd></div>\n                <div><dt>目標路線</dt><dd><strong class=\"case-detail-metric-value\">1 工作流程</strong><span>接收到打包輸出</span></dd></div>\n              </dl>\n            </div>\n          </article>\n          <article class=\"case-detail-timeline-item\">\n            <div class=\"case-detail-timeline-marker\"><span>02</span></div>\n            <div class=\"case-detail-stage-card\">\n              <p class=\"case-detail-stage-label\">合作單位</p>\n              <h3>匿名衛生服務業者</h3>\n              <p>合作單位計畫減少大型廢棄物運輸量，並在最終處置或下游轉移前回收可回收的部分。</p>\n              <dl class=\"case-detail-metrics\">\n                <div><dt>操作員類型</dt><dd><strong class=\"case-detail-metric-value\">1 衛生團隊</strong><span>轉運站運作</span></dd></div>\n                <div><dt>買家的顧慮</dt><dd><strong class=\"case-detail-metric-value\">2 目標</strong><span>音量減少與回收</span></dd></div>\n              </dl>\n            </div>\n          </article>\n          <article class=\"case-detail-timeline-item\">\n            <div class=\"case-detail-timeline-marker\"><span>03</span></div>\n            <div class=\"case-detail-stage-card\">\n              <p class=\"case-detail-stage-label\">實際限制</p>\n              <h3>該基層必須在轉運站的物流內運作</h3>\n              <p>該場址需要接收區、大型物料分區、設備通道、回收分餾物儲存區及卡車裝載區，且能在緊湊的作業範圍內設置。</p>\n              <dl class=\"case-detail-metrics\">\n                <div><dt>場地區域</dt><dd><strong class=\"case-detail-metric-value\">5 區域</strong><span>從貨櫃到裝卸區</span></dd></div>\n                <div><dt>版面類型</dt><dd><strong class=\"case-detail-metric-value\">緊湊型</strong><span>單一工作流程路徑</span></dd></div>\n              </dl>\n            </div>\n          </article>\n          <article class=\"case-detail-timeline-item\">\n            <div class=\"case-detail-timeline-marker\"><span>04</span></div>\n            <div class=\"case-detail-stage-card\">\n              <p class=\"case-detail-stage-label\">解法</p>\n              <h3>Lion One具有分離與打包介面的製程模組</h3>\n              <p>製程範圍結合破碎、篩選、氣流分離、輸送、選配磁性分離、打包介面及遠端控制 支援。</p>\n              <dl class=\"case-detail-metrics\">\n                <div><dt>製程模組</dt><dd><strong class=\"case-detail-metric-value\">4 模組</strong><span>壓碎 / 篩網 / 氣流 / 輸送</span></dd></div>\n                <div><dt>介面</dt><dd><strong class=\"case-detail-metric-value\">2 介面</strong><span>打包與遙控</span></dd></div>\n              </dl>\n            </div>\n          </article>\n          <article class=\"case-detail-timeline-item\">\n            <div class=\"case-detail-timeline-marker\"><span>05</span></div>\n            <div class=\"case-detail-stage-card\">\n              <p class=\"case-detail-stage-label\">前後對比</p>\n              <h3>參考圖顯示的是一條更可控的大型廢棄物路線</h3>\n              <div class=\"case-detail-comparison\">\n                <div><span>之前</span><strong>超大廢棄物以鬆散混合物質的形式移動</strong><p>運輸與分期壓力維持在縮小尺寸與回收檢查前維持高位。</p></div>\n                <div><span>之後</span><strong>減量、分離，準備下游處理</strong><p>參考影片展示了餵料、破碎、氣流分離、排放及打包介面的流程。</p></div>\n              </div>\n              <dl class=\"case-detail-metrics\">\n                <div><dt>影像範圍</dt><dd><strong class=\"case-detail-metric-value\">5 步驟</strong><span>供水至打包介面</span></dd></div>\n              </dl>\n            </div>\n          </article>\n        </div>\n      </section>\n\n      <section class=\"section case-detail-action-section industrial-rfq-section ai-layout-reference\" aria-label=\"案例操作\">\n        <div class=\"rfq-action-strip case-detail-action-strip\">\n          <a class=\"primary-button\" href=\"/contact\">請求參考包</a>\n          <a class=\"secondary-button\" href=\"/case-studies\">返回案例研究</a>\n        </div>\n      </section>\n    </main>"
}
